---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/layout/Section.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Apoti Development Association collects, uses, and protects your personal information.">
  <Section background="white" padding="lg">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-gray">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you use our website, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account information</strong> — name, email address, and password when you register</li>
        <li><strong>Donation information</strong> — payment details processed securely through Stripe</li>
        <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — name, email, and message content</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited and basic interaction data (no tracking cookies)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use It</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Process and receipt donations</li>
        <li>Manage your account and donation history</li>
        <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
        <li>Send updates about our programs (with your consent)</li>
        <li>Improve website functionality</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following services to operate this website:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — payment processing. Stripe handles all card data under their own <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — authentication and database hosting.</li>
        <li><strong>Sanity</strong> — content management system for website content.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — website hosting, CDN, and DDoS protection.</li>
        <li><strong>Resend</strong> — transactional email delivery (donation receipts, account verification).</li>
        <li><strong>Umami</strong> — privacy-friendly, cookie-free website analytics. No personal data is collected or shared.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use a single authentication session cookie to keep you logged in. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party analytics cookies.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain your account and donation data for as long as your account is active or as required for legal and financial record-keeping (typically 7 years for donation records). You may request deletion of your account data at any time.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for communications</li>
        <li>Export your data in a portable format</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For data requests or privacy questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@apotidev.org">info@apotidev.org</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</PageLayout>
